node.title: Homicide investigation into 48yo man's death in Te Awamutu
node.description: Police have launched a homicide investigation over a death at a Te Awamutu property.
node.content:
["Police have launched a homicide investigation over a death at a Te Awamutu property.", "", "
\nPhoto: RNZ / Patrice Allen\n
", "A 48-year old man died at an address in Hazelmere Crescent.", "Police were called to the property at 6.15am after reports of an altercation.", "The property was cordoned off and a scene examination was under way."]
